21:25.417 --> 21:27.214
You can count on us, Mr. President.

21:27.319 --> 21:29.810
Major Nougat, Gooey, Cocoa...

21:29.921 --> 21:32.151
put down those entertaining
Mattel products.

21:33.925 --> 21:37.053
Colonel Ga-taffy is up
to his old tricks.

21:37.162 --> 21:39.653
Let's power up!

21:40.966 --> 21:43.434
I can't believe
they canceled us for this-

21:43.535 --> 21:46.265
Shut up!
I'm trying to watch this.

21:46.371 --> 21:48.669
[All]
Chocolate away!

